#: zerver/lib/onboarding.py
msgid ""
"\n"
"You can [download](/apps/) the [mobile and desktop apps](/apps/).\n"
"Zulip also works great in a browser.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Vous pouvez [télécharger](/apps/) les [applications mobile et bureau](/"
"apps/).\n"
"Zulip fonctionne également très bien dans un navigateur.\n"

#: zerver/lib/onboarding.py
msgid ""
"\n"
"Go to [Profile settings](#settings/profile) to add a [profile picture](/help/"
"change-your-profile-picture)\n"
"and edit your [profile information](/help/edit-your-profile).\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Rendez-vous dans vos [paramètres de profil](#settings/profile) pour ajouter "
"[une image de profil](/help/change-your-profile-picture)\n"
"et modifier [vos informations de profil](/help/edit-your-profile).\n"

#: zerver/lib/onboarding.py
msgid ""
"\n"
"You can switch between [light and dark theme](/help/dark-theme), [pick your\n"
"favorite emoji set](/help/emoji-and-emoticons#change-your-emoji-set), "
"[change\n"
"your language](/help/change-your-language), and otherwise customize your "
"Zulip\n"
"experience in your [Preferences](#settings/preferences).\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Vous pouvez basculer entre le [thème clair et le thème sombre](/help/dark-"
"theme), [choisir votre \n"
"ensemble d'emojis préféré](/help/emoji-and-emoticons#change-your-emoji-set), "
"[changer\n"
"votre langue](/help/change-your-language), et personnaliser votre expérience "
"Zulip\n"
"dans vos [Préférences](#settings/preferences).\n"

#: zerver/lib/onboarding.py
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"Channels organize conversations based on who needs to see them. For "
"example,\n"
"it's common to have a channel for each team in an organization.\n"
"\n"
"[Browse and subscribe to channels]({settings_link}).\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Les canaux permettent d'organiser les conversations en fonction des "
"personnes qui doivent les voir. Par exemple,\n"
"il est courant d'avoir un canal pour chaque équipe au sein d'une "
"organisation.\n"
"\n"
"[Parcourir et s'abonner aux canaux]({settings_link}).\n"

#: zerver/lib/onboarding.py
msgid ""
"\n"
"[Topics](/help/introduction-to-topics) summarize what each conversation in "
"Zulip\n"
"is about. You can read Zulip one topic at a time, seeing each message in\n"
"context, no matter how many other conversations are going on.\n"
"\n"
"When you start a conversation, label it with a new topic. For a good topic "
"name,\n"
"think about finishing the sentence: “Hey, can we chat about…?”\n"
"\n"
"Check out [Recent conversations](#recent) for a list of topics that are "
"being\n"
"discussed.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"[Les conversations](/help/introduction-to-topics) résument le sujet de "
"chaque échange dans Zulip.\n"
"Vous pouvez lire Zulip une conversation à la fois, en voyant chaque message "
"dans\n"
"son contexte, quel que soit le nombre de conversations en cours.\n"
"\n"
"Lorsque vous démarrez une conversation, nommez-la avec un nouveau sujet. "
"Pour un bon titre,\n"
"pensez à compléter la phrase : « Salut, on pourrait parler de… ?»\n"
"\n"
"Consultez les [Conversations récentes](#recent) pour voir la liste \n"
"des sujets en cours.\n"

#: zerver/lib/onboarding.py
msgid ""
"\n"
"Zulip's [keyboard shortcuts](#keyboard-shortcuts) let you navigate the app\n"
"quickly and efficiently.\n"
"\n"
"Press `?` any time to see a [cheat sheet](#keyboard-shortcuts).\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Les [raccourcis clavier](#keyboard-shortcuts) de Zulip vous permettent de "
"naviguer\n"
"rapidement et efficacement dans l’application.\n"
"\n"
"Appuyez sur `?` à tout moment pour afficher la [liste des raccourcis]"
"(#keyboard-shortcuts).\n"

#: zerver/lib/onboarding.py
msgid ""
"\n"
"You can **format** *your* `message` using the handy formatting buttons, or "
"by\n"
"typing your formatting with Markdown.\n"
"\n"
"Check out the [cheat sheet](#message-formatting) to learn about spoilers, "
"global\n"
"times, and more.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Vous pouvez **formater** *votre* `message` à l’aide des boutons de formatage "
"pratiques,\n"
"ou en saisissant directement du Markdown.\n"
"\n"
"Consultez le [guide](#message-formatting) pour en savoir plus sur les "
"spoilers, les heures globales\n"
"et plus encore.\n"

#: zerver/lib/onboarding.py
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"Here are a few messages I understand: {bot_commands}\n"
"\n"
"Check out our [Getting started guide](/help/getting-started-with-zulip),\n"
"or browse the [help center](/help/) to learn more!\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Voici quelques messages que je comprends : {bot_commands}\n"
"\n"
"Consultez notre [guide de démarrage](/help/getting-started-with-zulip),\n"
"ou parcourez le [centre d'aide](/help/) pour en savoir plus !\n"

#: zerver/lib/onboarding.py
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"You can chat with me as much as you like! To\n"
"get help, try one of the following messages: {bot_commands}\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Vous pouvez discuter avec moi autant que vous le souhaitez !\n"
"Pour obtenir de l'aide, essayez l'un des messages suivants : {bot_commands}\n"

#: zerver/lib/onboarding.py
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"If anything is out of place, it’s easy to [move messages]"
"({move_content_another_topic_help_url}),\n"
"[rename]({rename_topic_help_url}) and [split]"
"({move_content_another_topic_help_url}) topics,\n"
"or even move a topic [to a different channel]"
"({move_content_another_channel_help_url}).\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Si un élément est mal placé, il est facile de [déplacer les messages]"
"({move_content_another_topic_help_url}),\n"
"[renommer]({rename_topic_help_url}) et [séparer]"
"({move_content_another_topic_help_url}) les conversations,\n"
"ou même de déplacer une conversation [vers un autre canal]"
"({move_content_another_channel_help_url}).\n"

#: zerver/lib/onboarding.py
msgid ""
"\n"
":point_right: Try moving this message to another topic and back.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
":point_right : Essayez de déplacer ce message vers une autre conversation, "
"puis de le remettre en place.\n"

#: zerver/lib/onboarding.py
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"Zulip is organized to help you communicate more efficiently. Conversations "
"are\n"
"labeled with topics, which summarize what the conversation is about.\n"
"\n"
"For example, this message is in the “{topic_name}” topic in the\n"
"#**{zulip_discussion_channel_name}** channel, as you can see in the left "
"sidebar\n"
"and above.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Zulip est conçu pour vous aider à communiquer plus efficacement. \n"
"Les conversations sont étiquetées avec des sujets qui résument leur "
"contenu.\n"
"\n"
"Par exemple, ce message se trouve dans la conversation « {topic_name} » \n"
"du canal #**{zulip_discussion_channel_name}**, comme vous pouvez le voir "
"dans la barre\n"
"latérale gauche et en haut de la page.\n"

#: zerver/lib/onboarding.py
msgid "welcome to Zulip!"
msgstr "bienvenue sur Zulip !"

#: zerver/lib/onboarding.py
msgid ""
"\n"
"You can read Zulip one conversation at a time, seeing each message in "
"context,\n"
"no matter how many other conversations are going on.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Vous pouvez lire Zulip une conversation à la fois, en voyant chaque message "
"dans son contexte, \n"
"quelle que soit l’activité des autres discussions.\n"

#: zerver/lib/onboarding.py
msgid ""
"\n"
":point_right: When you're ready, check out your [Inbox](/#inbox) for other\n"
"conversations with unread messages.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
":point_right : Lorsque vous êtes prêt, consultez votre [Boîte de réception](/"
"#inbox) \n"
"pour voir les autres conversations contenant des messages non lus.\n"

#: zerver/lib/onboarding.py
msgid ""
"\n"
"To kick off a new conversation, pick a channel in the left sidebar, and "
"click\n"
"the `+` button next to its name.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Pour démarrer une nouvelle conversation, choisissez un canal dans la barre "
"latérale gauche,\n"
"puis cliquez sur le bouton `+` à côté de son nom.\n"

#: zerver/lib/onboarding.py
msgid ""
"\n"
"Label your conversation with a topic. Think about finishing the sentence: "
"“Hey,\n"
"can we chat about…?”\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Donnez un sujet à votre conversation. Pensez à terminer la phrase : "
"« Salut,\n"
"on pourrait parler de… ? »\n"

#: zerver/lib/onboarding.py
msgid ""
"\n"
":point_right: Try starting a new conversation in this channel.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
":point_right : Essayez de démarrer une nouvelle conversation sur ce canal.\n"

#: zerver/lib/onboarding.py
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"\n"
":point_right:  Use this topic to try out [Zulip's messaging features]"
"({format_message_help_url}).\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
":point_right :  Utilisez cette conversation pour essayer les "
"[fonctionnalités de messagerie de Zulip]({format_message_help_url}).\n"

#: zerver/lib/onboarding.py
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"```spoiler Want to see some examples?\n"
"\n"
"````python\n"
"\n"
"print(\"code blocks\")\n"
"\n"
"````\n"
"\n"
"- bulleted\n"
"- lists\n"
"\n"
"Link to a conversation: #**{zulip_discussion_channel_name}>{topic_name}**\n"
"\n"
"```\n"
